window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The philosopher asks: \"Faced with the mutually exclusive choice between moral principle and the survival of your family, which is the correct path?\"</p> <p>Philosophers love to pose such questions, and in the day-to-day struggle, such thinkers rarely attain to a level of relevance rivaling that of the simple hunger pang. Their careful considerations dissipate under the leveled gun.</p> <p>We do not feel their disapproving gaze when The Others draw near.</p> <p>When the world sends doom, the survivors do not hesitate.</p> <p>The survivors do what is necessary.</p>"; 
